comments: Vucevic (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Jokic (DEN).
Millsap (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Isaac (ORL).
Harris (DEN) briefly engages with Fournier (ORL) as the two are moving over the screen, but Harris disengages by sliding his hands off.
Fournier (ORL) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Vucevic (ORL) moves to his right and delivers contact to Harris (DEN) which affects his ability to defend.
As Vucevic (ORL) begins to roll to the basket, Harris (DEN) grasps Vucevic's jersey and pulls his jersey away from his body affecting Vucevic's FOM.
Vucevic (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Murray (DEN).
Vucevic (ORL) does not establish a legal screening position as he does not firm up and hops into Craig (DEN) delivering contact that affects Craig's ability to defend the play.
Murray (DEN) maintains a legal pivot foot.
Fultz (ORL) makes marginal contact with Murray (DEN) during the driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) is in a legal screening position and does not deliver contact to Craig (DEN).
Harris (DEN) makes contact with Vucevic's (ORL) arm that affects Vucevic's ability to maintain control of the ball.
Ross (ORL) begins to dribble, Craig (DEN) firms up and maintains a legal defensive position on Ross on the perimeter.
Vucevic (ORL) is in a legal screening position and does not deliver contact to Harris (DEN).
As Vucevic (ORL) is attempting to set a screen, he and Jokic (DEN) briefly engage and disengage with each other.
Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Fultz (ORL).
Ross (ORL) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
Fultz (ORL) commits a take foul on Harris (DEN).
During the long rebound attempt, Gordon (ORL) and Millsap (DEN) briefly engage and disengage under the rim.
Gordon (ORL) does not inbound the ball within the allowed 5 seconds.
Murray (DEN) makes marginal contact with Fournier (ORL) during the driving shot attempt.
Isaac (ORL) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
Craig (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Fournier (ORL).
